<bibRefCitation author="GOGALA, M. &amp; RILAR, T." box="[614,841,909,933]" pageId="25" pageNumber="254" pagination="316 - 324" refId="ref16422" refString="GOGALA, M. &amp; T RILAR, T. 2004. Bioacoustic investigations and taxonomic considerations on the Cicadetta montana species complex (Homoptera: Cicadoidea: Tibicinidae). Anais da Academia Brasileira de Ciencias 76 (2): 316 - 324." type="journal article" year="2004">Gogala &amp;Trilar,2004</bibRefCitation>
